bill.summary: 5/6/1993--Introduced. Amends the Harmonized Tariff Schedule of the United States to suspend, through December 31, 1996, the duty on 3-(hydroxymethyl-phosphinyl)-1-propanoic acid, 2-hydroxyethyl ester (phospholan mixed with ethylene glycol).
